02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲用斜枱起飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一首國產<br />\n<br />\n你有無睇錯<br />\n<br />\n不嬲話用斜坡<br />\n<br />\n但家下竟然會安裝彈射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f553d3e4498f65cedf1c0ed0cead47620508d32","tid":102424,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:51:28.000Z","msg":"屌你班友仲應佢"},{"pid":"2863407c62b87d0701c43b805b4d52f7285fc8e3","tid":102424,"uid":53165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T20:50:20.000Z","msg":"蒸汽彈射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾多年前咁產物，而且講到最新科投咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e07f2e11992bba6159107b44e701d6b68a1db3","tid":102424,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T20:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蒸汽彈射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾多年前咁產物，而且講到最新科投咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英國係二戰前發明, <br />\n彈螺旋漿戰機<br />\n<br />\n80年前既發明"},{"pid":"f1d96792c5e3019bca0b9c101c6ae9e1ef6d0600","tid":102424,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T23:53:56.000Z","msg":"中國航母照抄俄國舊設計 專家：連缺點都複製<br />\n<br />\n2017-01-24 13:29<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國航母遼寧艦日前進行遠洋訓練引發關注，中國首艘自製航母也即將完工。軍事評論家指出，此艘航母以70年代俄製航母為藍本，「連缺點都複製」。<br />\n<br />\n根據《蘋果日報》報導，中國出身，現為加拿大人的《漢和》防務評論主編平可夫表示，中國自製的001A型航空母艦，採用的範本是俄國庫茲涅佐夫（Kuznetsov）號，屬於70年代的設計，與遼寧號是同一等級。<br />\n<br />\n平可夫談到，庫茲涅佐夫號在去年11月打擊IS時，不但沒有發揮作用，反而還損失Su33戰鬥機、MiG29UB各一架，直言「今日的庫茲涅佐夫，就是明日的001A型航母」。<br />\n<br />\n平可夫提到，依照001A型航母的外型、尺寸來看，完全是庫茲涅佐夫號的複製品，也因為是70年代的產物，中國並沒有更改已過時的設計，可說是連缺點都複製。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1957075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1957075&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7d6642c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1957075&h=7e569f86\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1957075</a>"},{"pid":"d59d991e4897917a9411559e5ca36a414c494385","tid":102424,"uid":71728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T23:57:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國航母照抄俄國舊設計 專家：連缺點都複製<br />\n<br />\n2017-01-24 13:29<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國航母遼寧艦日前進行遠洋訓練引發關注，中國首艘自製航母也即將完工。軍事評論家指出，此艘航母以70年代俄製航母為藍本，「連缺點都複製」。<br />\n<br />\n根據《蘋果日報》報導，中國出身，現為加拿大人的《漢和》防務評論主編平可夫表示，中國自製的001A型航空母艦，採用的範本是俄國庫茲涅佐夫（Kuznetsov）號，屬於70年代的設計，與遼寧號是同一等級。<br />\n<br />\n平可夫談到，庫茲涅佐夫號在去年11月打擊IS時，不但沒有發揮作用，反而還損失Su33戰鬥機、MiG29UB各一架，直言「今日的庫茲涅佐夫，就是明日的001A型航母」。<br />\n<br />\n平可夫提到，依照001A型航母的外型、尺寸來看，完全是庫茲涅佐夫號的複製品，也因為是70年代的產物，中國並沒有更改已過時的設計，可說是連缺點都複製。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1957075\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1957075&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7d6642c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1957075&h=7e569f86\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1957075</a></blockquote><br />\n中國除左抄仲識d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"1fcb90e05f2c405cf8db6f6e4612d3cd9c95838a","tid":102424,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:40:34.000Z","msg":"呢隻都應該要黎試，下隻先真係量產<br />\nbtw,  快撚啲支爆"},{"pid":"d92ebf75d712b01e6b369cc90494fe3916032086","tid":102424,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中國航母照抄俄國